# Copy to .env.local. Devnet only.

# Privy App ID (public, client-side). Create at dashboard.privy.io:
#   - enable Google login
#   - enable embedded Solana wallets (create on login)
#   - Solana devnet
# Until this is set, the end-user login screens show a "configure Privy" notice;
# the schedule and /admin screens work without it.
NEXT_PUBLIC_PRIVY_APP_ID=

# SERVER-ONLY. getProgramAccounts-capable devnet RPC (Helius). Read from
# ../../shroudline/.env at runtime if not set here — never exposed to the browser
# (the browser talks to /api/rpc, which proxies to this).
# HELIUS_RPC_URL=

# SERVER-ONLY TxLINE token. Read from ../../shroudline/.env if not set here.
# TXLINE_API_TOKEN=
